"{\"uid\": \"ocregister.com-2024-07-30-olympics-2024-athletes-cant-get-enough-of-this-chocolate-muffin-on-tiktok\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"e-Edition  Get the latest news delivered daily!\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 47, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Get the latest news delivered daily!\", \"from\": 51, \"to\": 87, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"e-Edition  Trending:  UPDATE:French bakery Coup de pates confirmed in aLinkedIn postthat they are the one's providing the viral chocolate muffins to the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 89, \"to\": 258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 118, \"end\": 124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999440931627458, \"rank\": 3.1717684929449035e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 242, \"end\": 257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.977041407390038e-15, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We knew our Maxi Muffin with Intense Chocolate was something special\\u2026 but we did not expect it to spark such a chocolate storm!\", \"from\": 259, \"to\": 387, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you all for the love!\\\"\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 416, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While it does not appear that there is a way for every day fans to purchase the muffins online, they did share that food service professionals can purchase the muffins on their e-commerce site.\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheOlympicshave been off to an exciting start.Team USAhas beenwinning medalsleft and right.\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 703, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But if you are only watching the summer games on your television, you are missing out on half the fun.\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Related:Check out our full coverage of the 2024 Olympics  Popularized during the Tokyo Olympics in 2021,Olympians are taking over TikTokto share their behind the scenes experiences and what it's really like to be an athlete living in the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1046, \"end\": 1061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.977041407390038e-15, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of the popular videos so far have been room tours, merchandise hauls and dining hall food reviews, the later of which has inspired a new craze of its own.\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic Village food review!\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1225, \"end\": 1240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.977041407390038e-15, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A little surprise at the end too!\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1287, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Smash like and subscribe for part 2\\u270c\\ud83c\\udffb#fyp#olympics#paris2024#olympictiktok#olympicvillage#foodreview@Olympics @paris2024 @Mr.Nicho  \\u266c original sound - Z7duckx_Music - Z7duckx_Music    Shortly after arriving to the Olympic Village, Henrik Christiansen, an Olympic Swimmer for Norway, shared a video of him reviewing the different foods he had tried so far in the dining hall.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1503, \"end\": 1518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.977041407390038e-15, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 1520, \"end\": 1539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.6621615443867334, \"rank\": 0.5102040816327192, \"text\": \"Henrik Christiansen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\"}, {\"begin\": 1564, \"end\": 1570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9999997052923825, \"rank\": 1.5552063564727566e-07, \"text\": \"Norway\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the items?\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A chocolate muffin.\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1700, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Insane.\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"11/10,\\\" he rated it.\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1730, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think you guys realize how good this stuff is#fyp#zipline#olympics#paris2024#olympictiktok#olympicvillage#muffins@Mr.Nicho  \\u266c original sound - I think you should leave shop    Since that initial video, Christiansen has posted 9 TikToks just about the chocolate muffins, which is over half of the 16 videos he's uploaded since arriving in Paris.\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 2085, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2080, \"end\": 2085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.982867752703766e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have chocolate muffin before GTA 6#fyp#olympics#paris2024#olympictiktok#olympicvillage#muffins#gta#gta6  \\u266c GTA San Andreas Theme (Remake) - Ben Morfitt (SquidPhysics)    From what Christiansen has shared, these are not your ordinary chocolate muffins.\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2120, \"end\": 2125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Theft_Auto\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"GTA 6\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Theft_Auto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Theft_Auto\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to being a chocolate batter with chocolate chunks on top, the inside appears to have melted chocolate, similar to a molten lava cake.\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2487, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When bae is looking like a snack#fyp#olympics#paris2024#olympictiktok#olympicvillage#muffins@Olympics @paris2024  \\u266c original sound - mywatchhistory    Christiansen's videos are inspiring fellow Olympic athletes to try the dessert themselves and share their own reviews.\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet another beautiful day in the Olympic Village#fyp#olympics#paris2024#olympictiktok#olympicvillage#muffins@Olympics @paris2024  \\u266c La belle vie - Sacha Distel    Olympic Swimmer Lewis Clareburt from New Zealand shared a video of him and Christiansen with a chocolate muffin in hand.\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 3043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2961, \"end\": 2972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.5924593759127758, \"rank\": 0.3272811692323643, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Guys i found him @Henrik Christiansen#olympics#paris2024  \\u266c Muffin Man - The Kiboomers    American rock climberColin Duffyalso shared a photo post of the treat with the caption reading \\\"You do not understand how good these muffins are.\\\"\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3281, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3136, \"end\": 3144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999682186177, \"rank\": 2.3808267456252437e-08, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"U.S. track and field star Gabby Thomas shared it was the best muffin she ever had, giving it a 9.8/10 rating, clarifying in her caption that she would have rated them higher but they had run out of them when she tried to get them earlier so she deducted points for that.\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3553, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3310, \"end\": 3322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9999913064562402, \"rank\": 8.69361921906588e-06, \"text\": \"Gabby Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Replying to @olivia random id rate it higher but they ran out when i tried to get it earlier so minus points for that  \\u266c original sound - Gabby Thomas    They are so good like ?\", \"from\": 3555, \"to\": 3732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"?\", \"from\": 3732, \"to\": 3733, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"?#olympics#olympicvillage#paris2024  \\u266c original sound - Lorena Pages    @Henrik Christiansen the#OlympicVillagechocolate muffins really are 11/10 !#Olympics#paris2024#olympicgames  \\u266c What Was I Made For?\", \"from\": 3733, \"to\": 3936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3790, \"end\": 3796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Lorraine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5146735907227154e-13, \"text\": \"Lorena\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Lorraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Lorraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"[From The Motion Picture \\\"Barbie\\\"] - Billie Eilish    this is a joke and i am an aid, not an athlete.\", \"from\": 3937, \"to\": 4038, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3964, \"end\": 3970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbie\", \"score\": 0.999999149560515, \"rank\": 8.504401091111773e-07, \"text\": \"Barbie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still at the olympics tho which is super cool \\ud83d\\ude42#olympics#paris2024#jo#jo2024#teamusa#italy#olympics2024  \\u266c original sound - Princess\\u2002Bunnyboo    As for viewers at home who are not able to visit the Olympic Village dining hall, some have taken it upon themselves to find out where they can get the chocolate muffins.\", \"from\": 4039, \"to\": 4354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4239, \"end\": 4254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.977041407390038e-15, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Others are sharing recipes that fans can make at home to soothe the craving.\", \"from\": 4355, \"to\": 4431, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"needing @Henrik Christiansen to get some deets on where the muffins are from, who makes them, how we can buy them, ANYTHING#olympics#parisolympics#olympics2024#muffins#muffinman#olympicswimming#olympicvillage  \\u266c original sound - jules \\ud83e\\udef6\\ud83c\\udffb    @Henrik Christiansen wdyt is it the same ?\", \"from\": 4433, \"to\": 4716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4444, \"end\": 4463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.6621615443867334, \"rank\": 0.5102040816327192, \"text\": \"Henrik Christiansen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"?#greenscreen#olympics#muffinman#baking  \\u266c original sound - kelin    @Henrik Christiansen get this man a chocolate muffin sponsorship and stat  \\u266c original sound - elaina    waiting for the next chocolate muffin vid @Henrik Christiansen  Recipe: Best Chocolate Muffins Adapted from twopeasandtheirpod.com and Eat What You Want by Gaby Dalkin  *Makes 6 jumbo muffins + 2 standard muffins  - 1 2/3 cups all pupose flower - 3/4 cup unsweetened cocoa powder - 1 tsp instant espresso powder  - 2 tsp baking powder - 1/2 tsp baking soda - 1 tsp salt - 1/2 cup hot water  - 1/2 cup granulated sugar - 1/2 cup light brown sugar, lightly packed - 1/3 cup avocado oil  - 2 large eggs + 1 egg yolk  - 2 tsp vanilla extract  - 3/4 cup greek yogurt  - 2 1/2 cups dark chocolate chips or chunks  Directions:  1.\", \"from\": 4716, \"to\": 5512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4790, \"end\": 4809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.6621615443867334, \"rank\": 0.5102040816327192, \"text\": \"Henrik Christiansen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\"}, {\"begin\": 4936, \"end\": 4955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.662162162161551, \"rank\": 0.5102040816327192, \"text\": \"Henrik Christiansen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henrik_Christiansen_(swimmer)\"}, {\"begin\": 5442, \"end\": 5454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strained_yogurt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"greek yogurt\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strained_yogurt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strained_yogurt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Preheat the oven to 375F.\", \"from\": 5513, \"to\": 5538, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Prepare a jumbo muffin tin or 12-cup cupcake tin with liners.\", \"from\": 5539, \"to\": 5600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2.\", \"from\": 5602, \"to\": 5604, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a small bowl,  combine the flour, \\u00bc cup of the cocoa powder, baking powder, baking soda, salt, and 2 cups of chocolate chips.\", \"from\": 5605, \"to\": 5733, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Make sure the chocolate chips are coated in flour so they distrubute evenly in the muffins.\", \"from\": 5734, \"to\": 5825, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"3.\", \"from\": 5827, \"to\": 5829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In another bowl, whisk together the remaining \\u00bd cup cocoa powder and espresso powder with the hot water until smooth.\", \"from\": 5830, \"to\": 5947, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"4.\", \"from\": 5948, \"to\": 5950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a large bowl, whisk together the eggs, avocado oil, sugar, greek yogurt, and vanilla.\", \"from\": 5951, \"to\": 6039, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6010, \"end\": 6015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sugar\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.4131102246461526e-12, \"text\": \"sugar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sugar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sugar\"}, {\"begin\": 6017, \"end\": 6029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strained_yogurt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"greek yogurt\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strained_yogurt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strained_yogurt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whisk in the cocoa powder mixture until combined.\", \"from\": 6040, \"to\": 6089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, fold in the flour mixture until just combined.\", \"from\": 6090, \"to\": 6142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"5.\", \"from\": 6144, \"to\": 6146, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Divide the batter into the muffin tins and top with the remaining chocolate chips.\", \"from\": 6147, \"to\": 6229, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"6.\", \"from\": 6231, \"to\": 6233, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bake jumbo muffins for 25 minutes and bake regular muffins for 15 minutes.\", \"from\": 6234, \"to\": 6308, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"7.\", \"from\": 6310, \"to\": 6312, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy!#ParisOlympics#chocolatemuffin#olympicvillage#easyrecipes#foryou  \\u266c original sound - michaela \\u0295\\uff1b \\u2022'\\u1d25\\u2022\\u00b4\\u0294    ignore my weird af hair, I am working from home#olympics#olympicvillage  \\u266c suono originale - \\ud835\\ude4e\\ud835\\ude49\\ud835\\ude40\\ud835\\ude3c\\ud835\\ude46\\ud835\\ude54\\ud835\\ude43\\ud835\\ude40\\ud835\\ude4d\\ud835\\ude4a\\ud835\\udff5\\ud835\\udfef    extreme olympic fomo @Henrik Christiansen#olympics#olympics2024#parisolympics2024#paris2024#olymipicmuffinman#olympicmuffins#swimming#2024#fyp#foryou#foryoupage  \\u266c sonido original - \\ud83d\\udc21    Prior to Coup de pates releasing an official statement, some eagle eye fans pieced together that the bakeries \\\"Maxi Muffin Chocolat Intense\\\" looked strikingly similar to the viral chocolate muffins.\", \"from\": 6313, \"to\": 6920, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Replying to @kelin @Henrik Christiansen we found them!!\", \"from\": 6922, \"to\": 6977, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"thank you @emily !\", \"from\": 6978, \"to\": 6996, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"!#greenscreen#olympics#paris2024#muffinman  \\u266c original sound - kelin    Copyright \\u00a9 2025 MediaNews Group\", \"from\": 6996, \"to\": 7100, \"entities\": []}]}"